d nachträglichen Übersicherung bei Kreditsicherheiten und zu den internationalen Entwicklungen im Recht der Kreditsicherheiten.  a["Current developments in the law on lending securities - on an international and national level. Internal and external rating"]The covered lectures and discussions treat issues of the practices of banks upon the adaptation of lending rates and the implementation of the "Basel II" rating method concerning the customer. In addition, it includes articles on the jurisdiction of the Federal tribunal on securities and guarantees, on initial and subsequent excessive safety of lending securities and on the international developments of the law on lending securities.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCredit ratingszGermanyvCongresses. 0aCreditxLaw and legislationzGermanyvCongresses. 0aSecurity (Law)zGermanyvCongresses. 4aKreditrecht. 4aKreditsicherung /Recht. 7aLAW / Corporate.2bisacsh1 aEidenmüller, Horst, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aEidenmüller, Horst, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrämer, Lutz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLangenbucher, Katja, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLangenbucher, Katja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLwowski, Hans-Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPfingsten, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWassermann, Henning, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aet al., , eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BO